lead_paragraph: Justin Nicolino gave up two hits in 7 1/3 innings in his season debut to lead the Miami Marlins to a 2-0 victory over the Los Angeles Dodgers on Wednesday night for their fourth straight win.

headline.print_headline: Nicolino Takes 2-Hitter Into 8th as Marlins Beat Dodgers 2-0
